name: LIVE SCREEN - PRINTING
description:
LIVE SCREEN-PRINTING
Want to have something special at your next event?
Want to wear something special from that very same event?

Exodus40 has a team of skilled printers and the right equipment to bring live screenprinting to your event
With up to four mobile stations and printers, we can handle any size crowd.

We can source your shirts and even prebrand them with your ministry identity ahead of time. 

Please contact us at 347-965-8175 or email info@exodus40.com for information about pricing and availability.
